snippet.title: How Janardhan Reddy Managed to Spent Rs 500 Crores on His Daughter's Wedding?

localized.description:
How Janardhan Reddy managed to spent so much on her daughter's wedding? Watch the truth behind 500 crore rupees spent in a wedding amid demonetisation of Rs 500 and 1000 notes. Mining king Janardhana Reddy spent more than five hundred crore rupees in his daughter Bramhani's marriage.
